[32m+[m[32m### **Pilot Project Contributions**[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mIf your team runs a delivery using the framework, consider contributing:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m1. A **Scope Document** that defined the work.[m
[32m+[m[32m2. The resulting **Codebase Guide** delta.[m
[32m+[m[32m3. A short **Case Study** (metrics table + lessons learned) under `docs/scopes/`.[m
[32m+[m[32m4. Any automation scripts or CI checks you built to enforce Delivery Tier rules.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mThese real-world artefacts are the fastest way to move the framework from theory to proven practice.[m
[32m+[m
